{"tid":892012,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"張學友係歌神，咁有無歌仙、歌俠、歌聖、歌王、歌霸、歌魔？","createTime":"2018-11-06T14:38:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T07:48:57.000Z","uid":206673,"like":3,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"595e7e084a1a1983b4b1053af3e4f8b7af866fa1","tid":892012,"uid":206673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T14:38:03.000Z","msg":"張學友係歌神，呢點毋庸置疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r4MsqMG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr4MsqMG.png&h=38e00f79&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WXAT5MH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWXAT5MH.png&h=01b218ca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zUqtadn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzUqtadn.png&h=0f01b0ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁有無歌仙、歌俠、歌聖、歌王、歌霸、歌魔？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我就覺得歌魔係郭富城<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o508UGe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo508UGe.png&h=1379c865&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NtNOUG1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNtNOUG1.png&h=e807f143&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢嘅勁歌熱舞真有一種魔力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MOsrXl0NRYo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMOsrXl0NRYo&d=kSqNWZ1VzRrKxwNx86kb2%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=72b45bd4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MOsrXl0NRYo</a><br />\n<br />\n歌仙就王菲，無論係歌定係人都充滿仙氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gumsqOu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgumsqOu.png&h=4bc5b228&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他又係邊個歌手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d0cdce8512287eb2c948d3f3f06efd95212814","tid":892012,"uid":206673,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T14:41:56.000Z","msg":"邊個負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c43df82e0176ccde1d4dea61661fba6daab2b8","tid":892012,"uid":61724,"like":12,"dislike":15,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T14:44:49.000Z","msg":"王菲1D都唔靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7a38cd4b404d0b7f2e09c0760bb124a014427b3","tid":892012,"uid":205996,"like":15,"dislike":15,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T14:45:21.000Z","msg":"如果計頂峰時期既王傑 就係歌神歌聖 四大天王都要企埋一邊"},{"pid":"7294123361f799e9140a4f495503b8bb8599c470","tid":892012,"uid":206673,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"d7a38cd4b404d0b7f2e09c0760bb124a014427b3","tid":892012,"uid":205996,"like":15,"dislike":15,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T14:45:21.000Z","msg":"如果計頂峰時期既王傑 就係歌神歌聖 四大天王都要企埋一邊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T14:46:49.000Z","msg":"我唔否認全盛時期王傑係好勁好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我又唔覺得佢超越到學友<br />\n最多排第二<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33ad1a3272d707d0de1d48a9e7fa2e1613b5a175","tid":892012,"uid":1249,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T14:46:55.000Z","msg":"歌俠 鄭少秋"},{"pid":"833f63c4f30fa24f412fed823645bc4b